snippet.title: Exoprimal - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Suit-up and face the dino swarms when Exoprimal launches July 14 2023!

Humanity has a second chance at survival – Play Exoprimal early on March 17-March 19 in the Open Beta Test, including full cross-platform matchmaking between Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Windows, PS5, PS4, and Steam!

Join the free Open Beta: https://www.exoprimal.com/en-us/networktest-obt/


Website: http://www.exoprimal.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/exoprimal
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/exoprimal
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com.exoprimal

#Exoprimal #Capcom #Gameplay
